race.description: Thank You Kooringal Rotary Hcp Heat Of The Rising Star
race.comment: RIVERBEND UNICORN (8) has returned in good order. Was a flashing light here last time when nabbing third and should be full steam ahead into this. Keatings takes over and rates a leading player. THINK I DO (6) was only 2L away when resuming at Nowra, then followed it up with a brave on-pace effort last time. Strips fitter and is drawn to advantage. Main danger. WINGS OF CARMEN (4) was much better last time at Albury when closing off strongly into third. Nearing peak now and will relish stepping out to the mile. CAYMAN ISLAND (5) was a determined winner here two back but went amiss last tie. Will be looking to utilise the low draw and gets in well with the claim. Will take reeling in if left alone in front.
